site bases. Comparison of $T_{1,2}$ measurements\nwith the site-by-site simulations indicate that cross-relaxation (partially)\naverages-out the variations in $\\tau_{R,T}$ and $T_{1,2}$ across the chain of\nlong-chain $n$-alkanes. This work also has implications on the role of\nnano-pore confinement on the NMR relaxation of fluids in the organic-matter\npores of kerogen and bitumen.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 23 Jan 2018 22:59:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-23"}
